text: Christophe Joseph Marie Dabiré (born 27 August 1948) is a Burkinabé politician. He was the Prime Minister of Burkina Faso from 24 January 2019 to 9 December 2021. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Burkina Faso
title: Christophe Joseph Marie Dabiré
